title: Diablo 2
description:
Diablo 2 is packaged with D2SE aka Diablo 2 mod manager

To run d2se.exe
If it dosn't start run D2VidTest.exe and select a video option then run d2se.exe
select the mod or version of diablo 2 you want to play


included mods are 
Median XL V005
Median XL ultamative V7 Realms support
Median XL ultamative V7 MultiRes support
other Median XL variants
